sourcesContent: import { useEffect, useState } from "react"; import Template from "../components/Template"; import swal from "sweetalert2"; import axios from "axios"; import config from "../config"; export default function Sale() { const [products, setProducts] = useState([]); useEffect(() => { }, []); const fetchData = async () => { try { await axios.get(config.api_path+'/product') } catch (e) { swal.fire({ title: "Error", text: e.message, icon: "error", }); } }; return ( <> ); }
